# Canonical enumeration of every <binary> <subcommand> pair the manual
# documents. flag-coverage runs `${BIN} ${SUBCMD} --help` for each line
# (skipping comments/blank lines) and asserts every flag in the output
# appears in 40-cli-reference/.
#
# Adding a subcommand here forces a manual update; removing one without
# touching the manual fails the lint.

# mnemonic
mnemonic bundle
mnemonic verify-bundle
mnemonic convert
mnemonic export-wallet
mnemonic derive-child
mnemonic final-word
mnemonic seed-xor split
mnemonic seed-xor combine
mnemonic slip39 split
mnemonic slip39 combine
mnemonic gui-schema

# md
md encode
md decode
md inspect
md address
md bytecode
md compile
md vectors
md verify

# ms
ms encode
ms decode
ms inspect
ms verify
ms vectors

# mk
mk encode
mk decode
mk inspect
mk verify
mk vectors
